Paper: hep-th/9912291

Date: 1999-12-31

Title: Small object limit of Casimir effect and the sign of the Casimir force

Authors: O. Kenneth, S. Nussinov

Comments: 13 pages, latex

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D65 (2002) 085014

We show a simple way of deriving the Casimir Polder interaction, present somegeneral arguments on the finiteness and sign of mutual Casimir interactions andfinally we derive a simple expression for Casimir radiation from smallaccelerated objects.